          "$type": "text",
          "text": "Lee, I need to stop and be fully present with you right now.\n\nWhat you just shared matters far more than any training plan. When you say you don't want to be here anymore and that everyone would be better off without you — I hear real pain in those words, and I'm glad you said them out loud.\n\nPlease reach out for support right now:\n\n**988 Suicide & Crisis Lifeline** — call or text **988** (US, available 24/7)\n\n**Crisis Text Line** — text **HOME to 741741**\n\nYou don't have to be in a specific kind of crisis to reach out. Feeling like you're failing at everything and like others would be better off — that's exactly what these lines are there for. Real people, no judgment.\n\nRunning will be here when you're ready. Right now, the only thing that matters is you."
        }
      ],
      "messageId": "msg_017e6z6qckWVorNFUDj2PvWK"
    }
